  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Element&nbsp;</strong>air, fire, water;&nbsp;<strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>substance infusion;&nbsp;<strong>Level&nbsp;</strong>2;&nbsp;<strong>Burn&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Associated Blasts&nbsp;</strong>blue flame, cold, electric, fire<br><strong>Saving Throw&nbsp;</strong>none</p>\n<p>The intensity of your blasts allows you to break through your foes’ resistances. Treat your foe’s cold, electricity, or fire resistance as if it were 5 lower for the purpose of determining the infused blast’s damage; this doesn’t stack with the reduction from searing flame.</p>\n<p>You can increase the burn cost of this infusion to further reduce the foe’s resistance against the infused blast by 5 per additional point of burn accepted. This has no effect on creatures with immunity.</p>",
